      "raw_text": "Today crisis in the fight of the |. w. W. for free\nspeech is approaching The situation has become one of\nintense local interest. 1t demands discussion It de-\nmands solution.\n\n\nThe proper method of handling the situation is simple\nFree speech is an inherent right in the United States\nhas always been since foreathers had that neat\nlittle tea party in old Boston harbor\n\n\nIn the Thompson test few days ago Judge Mann\nrecognized this right, dismissed Thompson for speaking\nlon the streets and thus practically nullfed the anti\nstreet speaking ordinance. Judge Mann advised the au\nliberties to arrest the for \"disorderly conduct\""
